{"tid":778801,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇啲好on9嘅朋友，佢講完d野你會想扮唔識佢？","createTime":"2018-08-14T03:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T10:20:44.000Z","uid":193530,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"875ec483ad2a6629b0e9edf10859c0c32c71ba6f","tid":778801,"uid":193530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:14:17.000Z","msg":"有一班番工識嘅朋友，入面有個好善良嘅肥婆，但佢成日被一條好口賤嘅肥仔串。<br />\n<br />\n有一次一齊去燒野食，見到有乳豬燒就叫咗嚟試下，咁就由個肥仔負責燒，到就快燒好個陣佢望住個肥婆講咗句：「你全家都被我燒晒啦，差你一個。」 跟著個肥婆即刻喊咗出嚟走咗去廁所。<br />\n我地成班人好想笑但又覺得個女仔好慘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有一次又係同依條肥仔仲有一班人一齊出街，食飯個陣冇人想理個肥仔，佢就自己坐係一邊。<br />\n<br />\n可能佢太悶，就過嚟搭嘴，咁啱個陣同個女仔傾緊計，個女仔就問我地平時會做啲咩，我地答完佢之後個肥仔就問個女仔做咩唔問佢平時會做啲咩，個女仔聽到就話：「好啦，咁你平時會做啲咩呀？」<br />\n個肥仔就答佢：「無呀，我平時咪鍾意睇下書，打下飛機咁囉。」<br />\n個女仔即刻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後無再理佢<br />\n我地係隔離聽到全部個樣都 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁樣樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到底要乜野嘅成長環境先可以造就到依種人出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d504c0b82458c581b45e21c952e5ebd32b5703a7","tid":778801,"uid":173480,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:21:16.000Z","msg":"通常呢啲肥鳩都係以為自己好charm, 自己呢種唔係肥，係健碩，所以特別有自信"},{"pid":"3e5efa65db43c6c8e803660ad82245c41d6023b6","tid":778801,"uid":144784,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:23:26.000Z","msg":"個肥仔一定係鍾意個肥婆先會蝦佢"},{"pid":"eaad75f88a65fed4a1cde1162ee2381f35c4766e","tid":778801,"uid":76098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:27:53.000Z","msg":"有冇人當面屌鳩過個肥仔?"},{"pid":"6a9a038dd6aad46f6e2deef36a607eab12a41889","tid":778801,"uid":71140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"396c9cd0f87762fcb06dbcff3bfefbaa706225ab","tid":778801,"uid":31384,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:29:11.000Z","msg":"佢老味<br />\n去haagen daz買雪糕食<br />\n佢用食家口吻問人哋<br />\n&quot;今日啲雪糕凍唔凍?&quot;"},{"pid":"52d28464317ca42b88169baa71e8a2b6a201ad9d","tid":778801,"uid":195169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:35:43.000Z","msg":"諗起ERIC CARTMAN <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肥仔應該自以為幽默, 自信心爆棚果類<br />\n就算搵人中柒佢佢都唔會改"},{"pid":"60fabc3a04e8432c62ab5031a26bc287f5ce470c","tid":778801,"uid":141297,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"第一個幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第二段就真係on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbfef3623ee45660751a69477a36384e2d9cfe8","tid":778801,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"396c9cd0f87762fcb06dbcff3bfefbaa706225ab","tid":778801,"uid":31384,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:29:11.000Z","msg":"佢老味<br />\n去haagen daz買雪糕食<br />\n佢用食家口吻問人哋<br />\n&quot;今日啲雪糕凍唔凍?&quot;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:47:46.000Z","msg":"人地有冇答佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394a9ca9f63c4b54b1bd2ba410a4a2b0f879eddc","tid":778801,"uid":199861,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:51:28.000Z","msg":"既然個肥仔咁戇鳩好心你就屌柒佢啦<br />\n望住人哋畀佢蝦都唔出聲<br />\n淨係識得上嚟開post屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31bd610c927d8b0169f9f117c55daa120084f73","tid":778801,"uid":24265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:58:54.000Z","msg":"第一個笑到仆街喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二個真係唔想理佢<img sr